{"tid":2242164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[陳同佳2.0]無牌駕駛車死咗人無代價仲風流快活","createTime":"2020-10-13T21:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T08:15:32.000Z","uid":308464,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c2eadd0cded82da6e2d373e3c5e14edf61ac09e3","tid":2242164,"uid":308464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T21:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nb6h1O8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnb6h1O8.png&h=c0fb80fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無牌駕駛害死人，過咗去一年，家人依舊在悲痛當中，依家佢畏罪潛逃，走咗佬，一啲懲罰都無。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n青衣長青隧道今日(26日)凌晨發生致命交通意外，警方經調查揭私家車姓鄭（30歲）男司機無牌駕駛，警方以涉危險駕駛導致他人死亡、以及無牌駕駛將其拘捕。事件中，姓嚴（21歲）女子傷重送院後不治；另外，1男1女乘客受傷，司機未有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，前座姓李（28歲)男乘客仍清醒，事後被送院，姓鄭司機則在現場協助警方調查；據悉，警方現場為鄭進行酒精呼氣測試，證實曾有飲酒但未有超標。據悉，其後有車禍傷者友人馳車抵達現場情緒激動，一度喝罵在場記者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2506208/長青隧道1死2傷致命交通意外%E3%80%80司機揭無牌駕駛導致他人死亡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2506208%2F%E9%95%B7%E9%9D%92%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%931%E6%AD%BB2%E5%82%B7%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%25E3%2580%2580%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%8F%AD%E7%84%A1%E7%89%8C%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%B4%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=87775ca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2506208/長青隧道1死2傷致命交通意外%E3%80%80司機揭無牌駕駛導致他人死亡</a>"},{"pid":"d1fc2199da79d65769637267b119f160ee999302","tid":2242164,"uid":308464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T21:25:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738f67067221ba9ba00c9f9e7655a40b62fe19bb","tid":2242164,"uid":175258,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T21:33:13.000Z","msg":"關我咩事"},{"pid":"4ce4d2